  "tags": ["preview-factory", "phase-f"],
  "notes": "Called asynchronously by workflow 01. Searches Outscraper, scores confidence, routes: >=0.7 auto-proceeds to generation; 0.1-0.69 emits disambiguation card via Realtime; <0.1 emits extended form prompt. The /building page listens to build_progress via Supabase Realtime. For disambiguation/no-match paths, the frontend submits the chosen business back via a separate endpoint (not in this workflow) which then calls workflow 03 directly."
